name: PRST
description: Electronic music venue (also known as Praterstrasse club) in Leopoldstadt district near Nestroyplatz. Features themed nights and DJ performances in underground arches atmosphere.

name: Puff
description: Bar housed in former brothel in Mariahilf district near Museumsquartier. Features unique atmosphere with LED lighting and vintage cocktail machines. Known for quality cocktails and eclectic decor.

name: Purple Club Vienna
description: Premier club and event venue in downtown Vienna offering unique events, top-tier gastronomy, and breathtaking atmosphere. Suitable for private parties, corporate events, and weekly club nights.

name: Queer:beat
description: Vienna's biggest queer Pop Party featuring multiple DJs for young, dance-crazy LGBTQ+ crowd. Recurring party event at various venues throughout Vienna.

name: Ragnarhof
description: Rock club and concert venue hosting wide range of musical genres. Features outdoor seating and casual atmosphere. Note: Some sources indicate possible closure - verify status before visiting.

name: Reigen Live
description: Club, bar and restaurant in 14th district featuring over 100 live concerts annually, specializing in blues and jazz. Serves Viennese cuisine with concerts typically starting at 20:30, doors at 19:30. U4 subway stop in front.

name: Rote Bar
description: Cultural bar within Volkstheater hosting queer and pop-discursive events. Fixed place in Viennese cultural life for years. Open daily evenings.

name: Roxy
description: Operating since 1991, one of Vienna's main venues for Soul, Funk, R'n'B and Hip-Hop. Hidden behind unassuming blue door in Wieden district. Open weekend nights and before holidays.
opening_hours: Fri, Sat and before holidays from 23:00

name: Porgy & Bess
description: Jazz and music club in Innere Stadt, one of the top ten jazz clubs in Europe. Features diverse program with live music daily. Office hours for tickets Monday-Friday 10:00-15:00.

name: Prater Dome
description: Austria's largest disco at Riesenradplatz in Prater featuring three floors, twelve bars in six areas. Music ranges from techno, house, EDM, DnB, trance, R'n'B and hip hop to party classics from 1990s and 2000s. Entry from age 18.
